Mom?

01:02.650 --> 01:05.652
Dad?

01:08.757 --> 01:10.758
Mom!

01:14.196 --> 01:16.764
Mom?

01:16.832 --> 01:20.144
Mom!
Mom, open the door!

01:21.665 --> 01:23.566
Mom!

01:23.667 --> 01:25.535
What is it, Norman?

01:25.602 --> 01:29.505
It's dad.
He's--hurry!

01:39.650 --> 01:43.085
Dad? Dad? Dad?

01:43.153 --> 01:45.154
Dad...

01:52.296 --> 01:53.229
Norman...

02:00.571 --> 02:02.538
Norman?

02:05.142 --> 02:08.144
Norman.

02:16.320 --> 02:20.323
Oh, honey.
I'm so sorry.

02:21.592 --> 02:23.659
Dad.

02:34.646 --> 02:44.751
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrections by honeybunny</font>
